headline: Treasury Yields Little Changed Ahead of ADP Jobs Report
summary: Treasury yields were little changed from Monday as U.S. lawmakers approved funding legislation to end a partial government shutdown.

headline: Treasury Yields Rise as Trump Pushes Lawmakers to End Shutdown
summary: Treasury yields rise slightly as markets face another data blackout while President Trump pushes Republicans to quickly end the partial government shutdown. The December JOLTS report won't be published today, as previously scheduled.
